{
  "doc_id": "38152",
  "text": "In today's world, urbanization and advances in technology have influenced the current lifestyle and have made a sedentary life, obesity and unhealthy nutrition habit [CITATION_1] . A healthy life style is known as an important factor in primary prevention for diseases [CITATION_2] . Many of unhealthy behaviors are associated with serious disease such as heart or respiratory disease, types of cancer and psychological disorder in later life [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] . Healthy lifestyle is a significant factor in cancer etiologic and prevention of cancer [CITATION_5] . Known lifestyle factors include physical activity, sleep pattern, social and family relationship, spirituality, safety, relaxation, nutrition and others [CITATION_6] .",
